  "detailed_description": "Dodge the bullets, shoot the enemies, defeat the bosses! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702810/extras/0e281b4ec0b083a4de99f85419679df7.avif?t=1572327846\" width=600 height=124 /></span><br><br>Take to the skies for an endless-arcade shooter that is fast, furious and formidable!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect over 200 daring pilots over 20 different terrains.<br></li><li>Change the intensity from Scouty to Screamy, if you dare!<br></li><li>Earn a multitude of achievements <br></li><li>Challenging daily missions<br></li><li>Guns! Missiles! Badgers!</li></ul><br><strong>Get flying now!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702810/extras/2010715f9ae14f57703235341d1634f1.poster.avif?t=1572327846\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702810/extras/2010715f9ae14f57703235341d1634f1.webm?t=1572327846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702810/extras/2010715f9ae14f57703235341d1634f1.mp4?t=1572327846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Dodge the bullets, shoot the enemies, defeat the bosses! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702810/extras/0e281b4ec0b083a4de99f85419679df7.avif?t=1572327846\" width=600 height=124 /></span><br><br>Take to the skies for an endless-arcade shooter that is fast, furious and formidable!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect over 200 daring pilots over 20 different terrains.<br></li><li>Change the intensity from Scouty to Screamy, if you dare!<br></li><li>Earn a multitude of achievements <br></li><li>Challenging daily missions<br></li><li>Guns! Missiles! Badgers!</li></ul><br><strong>Get flying now!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702810/extras/2010715f9ae14f57703235341d1634f1.poster.avif?t=1572327846\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702810/extras/2010715f9ae14f57703235341d1634f1.webm?t=1572327846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/702810/extras/2010715f9ae14f57703235341d1634f1.mp4?t=1572327846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
